net.richarddawkins.watchmaker.morphs.concho.genome.type

Enum ClassicSnail

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ClassicSnail>
      • net.richarddawkins.watchmaker.morphs.concho.genome.type.ClassicSnail
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ClassicSnail>

    public enum ClassicSnail
extends java.lang.Enum<ClassicSnail>
    Dawkins did not provide explicit mutation probabilities in all cases. I have used the value "100" where he did not provide a value. This should probably be changed to whatever the initialization value is for mutProb in the Pascal sources.
    Author:
    Alan Canon
